{
  "stem": "26609.20",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my brother-- she lived not far from me-- and he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] second after her, was my brother, Josef.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I loved him dearly, I think better than any other of my sisters or brothers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he, he had a young wife and first child, only a few-- I think, a few months old.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the Soviets left and the Germans started on the other side of Poland, still not in Lwow, but there were rumors that already-- that they killed-- didn't know exactly-- but people fled-- Jewish people fled from the-- these were the Soviet [INAUDIBLE], as they called him.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They told stories that first they kill all Jewish males.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if anyone can run away, should do so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother talked with his wife, and she advised him to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most young men ran to Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's a long way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People didn't think-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they thought-- first they-- they ran away first, running on foot to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was eastern Lwow, eastern Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a long way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Russians came slowly on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they've seen a lot of people on the streets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they, from the air, from the planes, they shot-- started to shoot them all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And never heard of him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his wife-- another thing that people were not quite normal-- took the baby of about two months.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't even remember the name as the baby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember her name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was Rosa Kimmel from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they lived-- she was born in a small town near the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from Lwow to the Russian border, kilo-- hundreds and hundreds of kilometers.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
